  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multiple model sizes (1.8B, 7B, 14B, 72B parameters)",
    "Base and chat-aligned model variants",
    "Quantization support (GPTQ Int4/Int8, KV cache quantization)",
    "Fine-tuning methods (full-parameter, LoRA, Q-LoRA)",
    "Function calling and tool use capabilities",
    "OpenAI-compatible API server",
    "Long context support (up to 32K tokens)",
    "Multi-language support (Chinese and English focus)",
    "Flash Attention 2 support",
    "Batch inference optimization"
